        {
          "title": {
            "_text": "光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」"
          },
          "link": {
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30591"
          },
          "comments": {
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30591#respond"
          },
          "dc:creator": {
            "_cdata": "萌朧雪猴"
          },
          "pubDate": {
            "_text": "Mon, 04 Nov 2024 08:49:51 +0000"
          },
          "category": [
            {
              "_cdata": "模型周邊"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "周邊情報"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "聯名酒"
            },
            {
              "_cdata": "賽馬娘Pretty Derby"
            }
          ],
          "guid": {
            "_attributes": {
              "isPermaLink": "false"
            },
            "_text": "https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/?p=30591"
          },
          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>由位於佐賀縣鹿島市的「光武酒造場」，攜手跨媒體IP《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》，以其中擬人化馬娘「谷野美酒」角色為印象，以「利口酒」形式推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30591\">光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">由位於佐賀縣鹿島市的「光武酒造場」，攜手跨媒體IP《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》，以其中擬人化馬娘「谷水琴蕾」角色為印象，以「利口酒」形式推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-1024x1024.webp\" alt=\"kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01\" class=\"wp-image-30592\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 5\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-300x300.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-150x150.webp 150w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-768x768.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-75x75.webp 75w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-350x350.webp 350w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-750x750.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01.webp 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">於元禄元年（1688年）創業，位於佐賀縣「肥前濱宿」地區的「光武酒造場」，原本主要生產燒酎和日本酒，但在成功研發出日式精釀琴酒後，從2020年起開始販售這類產品。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"680\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164034/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet05-1024x680.webp\" alt=\"kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet05\" class=\"wp-image-30596\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 6\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164034/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet05-1024x680.webp 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164034/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet05-300x199.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164034/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet05-768x510.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164034/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet05-1536x1020.webp 1536w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164034/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet05-750x498.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164034/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet05-1140x757.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164034/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet05.webp 1716w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">先前在<a href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/24812\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/24812\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">「台北琴酒節Gin Festival Taipei 2024」</a>上，和飲九九攤位上便帶來了由「光武酒造場」推出的「XYGIN Pink Silver 城市獵人粉銀琴酒」、「XYGIN Black Gold 城市獵人黑金琴酒」等聯名琴酒款商品。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/02133907/2024ginfestivaltaipeiwain99twevent04.jpg\" alt=\"2024ginfestivaltaipeiwain99twevent04\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 7\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/02133905/2024ginfestivaltaipeiwain99twevent03.jpg\" alt=\"2024ginfestivaltaipeiwain99twevent03\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 8\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/02133913/2024ginfestivaltaipeiwain99twevent07.jpg\" alt=\"2024ginfestivaltaipeiwain99twevent07\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 9\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/13964\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/13964\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》的手遊</a>在台灣也有不少人遊玩，並曾多次在線下規畫大型宣傳廣告。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/umakomoejoymetrotaipeiximen10.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 10\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/umakomoejoymetrotaipeiximen12.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 11\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/umakomoejoymetrotaipeiximen03.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 12\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">此次，光武酒造場為了讓更多人能享受其日式精釀琴酒，攜手《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》，將馬娘「谷水琴蕾(Tanino Gimlet)」角色的設計元素融入瓶身，並以琴酒為基底製作出這款利口酒「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-1024x1024.webp\" alt=\"kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01\" class=\"wp-image-30592\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 5\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-300x300.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-150x150.webp 150w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-768x768.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-75x75.webp 75w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-350x350.webp 350w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01-750x750.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164007/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet01.webp 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」主要材料為蒸餾酒（日本國內製造）、萊姆果汁、葡萄糖果糖漿（日本國內製造），酒精濃度則為25％，這款酒在萊姆清爽的酸味下，帶出琴酒辛香的餘韻，仿佛感受到「谷水琴蕾」的強勁衝刺。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">瓶身亮眼的突顯出「谷水琴蕾」的帥氣，瓶口配有致敬她身穿決勝服時所佩戴的項鍊；瓶子則放置於印有象徵「破壞神」之異名圖案的特製原創外盒。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"341\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164014/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02-341x1024.webp\" alt=\"kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02\" class=\"wp-image-30593\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 14\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164014/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02-341x1024.webp 341w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164014/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02-100x300.webp 100w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164014/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02-768x2305.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164014/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02-512x1536.webp 512w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164014/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02-682x2048.webp 682w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164014/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02-750x2251.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164014/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02-1140x3421.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164014/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet02-scaled.webp 853w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 341px) 100vw, 341px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164030/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet04-768x1024.webp\" alt=\"kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet04\" class=\"wp-image-30595\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 15\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164030/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet04-768x1024.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164030/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet04-225x300.webp 225w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164030/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet04-1152x1536.webp 1152w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164030/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet04-1536x2048.webp 1536w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164030/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet04-750x1000.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164030/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet04-1140x1520.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164030/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet04-scaled.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"387\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164022/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03-387x1024.webp\" alt=\"kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03\" class=\"wp-image-30594\" title=\"光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」 16\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164022/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03-387x1024.webp 387w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164022/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03-113x300.webp 113w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164022/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03-768x2031.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164022/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03-581x1536.webp 581w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164022/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03-774x2048.webp 774w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164022/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03-750x1983.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164022/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03-1140x3015.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04164022/kinpajpPrettyDerbyTaninoGimlet03-scaled.webp 968w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 387px) 100vw, 387px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」，容量為720ml，日幣含稅價為6,100円，限量5000瓶並已於日本開放預購。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">※產品照片及規格可能與實際商品有所不同。</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">© Cygames, Inc.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">※飲酒過量，有害（礙）健康；酒後不開車，安全有保障 </p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.hizennya.com/c/bd/korabo/3008\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.hizennya.com/c/bd/korabo/3008\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」官方商品頁面</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30591\">光武酒造場X《賽馬娘 Pretty Derby》 推出聯名酒款「Gimlet by Tanino Gimlet」</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
