          "description": {
            "_cdata": "<p>東映動畫活動專區公開，「THE FIRST SLAMDUNK POP UP STORE(灌籃高手期間限定快閃店)」台中，將自11月15日起在新光三越台中開設。</p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30588\">「THE FIRST SLAMDUNK POP UP STORE」台中 將於11月15日起在新光三越台中開設</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
          "content:encoded": {
            "_cdata": "\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">東映動畫活動專區公開，「THE FIRST SLAMDUNK POP UP STORE(灌籃高手期間限定快閃店)」台中，將自11月15日起在新光三越台中開設。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-1024x1024.webp\" alt=\"2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01\" class=\"wp-image-30589\" title=\"「THE FIRST SLAMDUNK POP UP STORE」台中 將於11月15日起在新光三越台中開設 17\" srcset=\"https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-300x300.webp 300w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-150x150.webp 150w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-768x768.webp 768w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-75x75.webp 75w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-350x350.webp 350w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-750x750.webp 750w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01-1140x1140.webp 1140w, https://imgmoelong.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/moelongnews/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/04014659/2024toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoretaichungprologue01.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">2023年時便在新光三越信義店A11一樓開設過<a href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/16121\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/16121\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">快閃店</a>。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://img.moelong.com/images/2023toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoreevent/2023toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoreevent05.jpg\" alt=\"2023toeianimtwslamdunkpopupstoreevent05\" title=\"「THE FIRST SLAMDUNK POP UP STORE」台中 將於11月15日起在新光三越台中開設 18\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">「THE FIRST SLAMDUNK POP UP STORE」台中，從2024年11月15日－12月15日，於新光三越台中中港店10F天空劇場開設，為免費入場。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/toei.anim.tw.event\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/toei.anim.tw.event\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">東映動畫活動專區 FB粉絲專頁</a></p>\n<p>這篇文章 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews/archives/30588\">「THE FIRST SLAMDUNK POP UP STORE」台中 將於11月15日起在新光三越台中開設</a> 最早出現於 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.moelong.com/moelongnews\">萌朧動漫情報網</a>。</p>\n"
          },
